node.text: @avchiang it’s one if my favourite places in SG, so wish to go back and spend a whole day there!

Throwback to @gardensbythebay ‘s last floral exhibition 🌸

This was taken on 15 March ‘20, about 3 weeks before the circuit breaker period started. There was already a limit imposed on the number of visitors allowed into the domes. Almost half of the people we saw already donned on 😷, things still seemed very normal. Fast-forward 2+ months later, we’re more or less accustomed to the new norm. 
Freedom is and has always been such a luxury. Side note, I haven’t been to the Floral Fantasy yet and would love to visit when things are looking better!

#gardensbythebaysingapore #gardensbythebayflowerdome
@laipoh yes!!! Seen so many pretty OOTD shots here😂
I always wanting to visit floral fantasy 😍 hope I could visit when the pandemic is over
let’s go floral fantasy tgt next time!
@mo0n_cake it is!!!! Airconditioning is a bonus 😂
@elainelim__ it sure looks like it from photos!
Yes you should! Floral fantasy is amazing!! 😍
@overpackedsuitcase hope all this blows over soon!
@avchiang I hope so too sweetie 💕💕hope you’ve been doing okay 🤗
@cozytravelview it is! You must visit when you’re in a Singapore next time!
@coriechuhealing yes @gardensbythebay is a must visit in Singapore!😍
@avchiang it’s one if my favourite places in SG, so wish to go back and spend a whole day there!
Love this place! Its really amazing how the nature combined with modern architecture💚✨
